Text: Sebagai seorang content creator, in order to have a long relationship with clients, and make sure both sides dapat win-win situations, this is what i do (Thread) :
Translated Text: Sebagai seorang content creator, in order to have a long relationship with clients, and make sure both sides dapat win-win situations, this is what i do (Thread) :

Text: 1. First and foremost, product or service tu aku sendiri kena guna and suka, baru i proceed to promote. It is unethical to promote and claim something is good kalau you sendiri tak pernah guna benda tu. Because people spend their hard earned money to follow your endorsement
Translated Text: 1. First and foremost, product or service tu aku sendiri kena guna and suka, baru i proceed to promote. It is unethical to promote and claim something is good kalau you sendiri tak pernah guna benda tu. Because people spend their hard earned money to follow your endorsement

Text: 2. Once agreed, I akan tanya client what is their expectation and apa end goal dia nak dari campaign tu. Dia nak org beli barang tu (call to action), nak org kenal brand dia (brand awareness), atau dia nak sampaikan sesuatu message (mcm CSR etc)
Translated Text: 2. Once agreed, I will ask the client what is their expectation and what is the end goal he wants from the campaign. He wants people to buy the item (call to action), wants people to know his brand (brand awareness), or he wants to convey a message (such as CSR etc.)

Text: 3. Bila dh tahu apa client nak, I will tell them straight forward samada benda dia nak tu realistic ke tak. Sbb kadang2 brand dah terbiasa work with tv commercial, and they assume social media works the same way. Unfortunately tak sama
Translated Text: 3. If I already know what the client wants, I will tell them straight forward whether the thing he wants is realistic or not. Because sometimes brands are used to working with TV commercials, and they assume social media works the same way. Unfortunately not the same

Text: 4. Bila dah buat content and dpt audience, i should know apa my audience suka, apa audience tak suka, etc. and bila brand datang dengan sesuatu product, i straight forward kena bagitau “maaf saya x boleh promote mesin ni sbb harga dia di luar kemampuan my audience”
Translated Text: 4. When I've created content and got an audience, I should know what my audience likes, what the audience doesn't like, etc. and when a brand comes with a product, I straight forward have to say "sorry I can't promote this machine because its price is beyond my audience's ability"

Text: 5. “kalau i promote jugak, you takkan dpt customers”. you need to explain the demographic details. so adakah discussion habis kat situ? tak. you can ask them “do you have another machine yg cheaper price? i think machine ni lagi sesuai”
Translated Text: 5. "If I promote too, you won't get customers". you need to explain the demographic details. so does the discussion end there? not. you can ask them "do you have another machine with a cheaper price?" I think this machine is more suitable"

Text: 6. by suggesting to your client (di support dengan real analytics) diaorg akan lebih fhm why your plan will work better. so bila nak go for cara nak promote, ini pn main peranan
Translated Text: 6. by suggesting to your client (supported with real analytics) diaorg will be more fhm why your plan will work better. so if you want to go for ways to promote, this also plays a role

Text: 7. bila you nak promote campaign tu, apa storyboard, platform apa yg sesuai, adakah ni too hard sell, adakah ni too soft sell, adakah timing salah, what if time ni org tak ada duit sbb tengah bulan belum dpt gaji etc
Translated Text: 7. when you want to promote the campaign, what storyboard, what platform is suitable, is this too hard sell, is this too soft sell, is the timing wrong, what if this time people don't have money because in the middle of the month they haven't been paid etc.

Text: 8. katakanlah client kata “tak apa, we understand the circumstances but we still want to proceed walaupun result tak bagus”, then it’s ok to proceed. because at least they lowered down their expectation already
Translated Text: 8. katakanlah client kata “tak apa, we understand the circumstances but we still want to proceed walaupun result tak bagus”, then it’s ok to proceed. because at least they lowered down their expectation already

Text: 9. Working with brands is a long term networking. bila tolong each other, both sides akan happy. So far alhamdulillah all my clients happy with their results. Kalau ada any suggestion pn i akan bagi to my clients for free. it’s all about win-win for both parties 🤝
Translated Text: 9. Working with brands is a long term networking. bila tolong each other, both sides akan happy. So far alhamdulillah all my clients happy with their results. Kalau ada any suggestion pn i akan bagi to my clients for free. it’s all about win-win for both parties 🤝
